references: Corresponding results are shown in Table 5, we can see that FL-AGCNS has much better performance than CrotrollerEO and ClientEO. This result shows us the significance and necessity of maintaining EA optimizers in both the controller and clients under FL scenarios. As discussed in Section¬†3.3, EA optimizers in each client contribute much in avoiding local optimums and improving federated performance in the early generations, whereas the controller‚Äôs EA optimizer performs better on population optimization in the later generations. Two kinds of optimizers optimize population from different aspects in FL-AGCNS and show good performance in different stages. Therefore, their combination is meaningful and necessary.
